title: Carey Mulligan talks baby daughter at 'Suffragette' premiere
text:
> Top News Carey Mulligan talks baby daughter at 'Suffragette' premiere Writer Abi Morgan, from left, Helen Pankhurst, producer Alison Owen, Carey Mulligan, director Sarah Gavron and producer Faye Ward attend the premiere for "Suffragette" at the Paris Theatre on Monday, Oct. 12, 2015, in New York.
